{
  "meta": {
    "is_partial": true,
    "description": "Order Detail - Confirm Bank Deposit Modal (무통장 입금확인)"
  },
  "id": "modal_confirm_deposit",
  "type": "composite",
  "name": "Modal",
  "props": {
    "title": "$t:sirsoft-ecommerce.admin.order.detail.modal.confirm_deposit.title",
    "size": "md",
    "closeOnOverlayClick": false,
    "closeOnEscape": false
  },
  "children": [
    {
      "type": "basic",
      "name": "Div",
      "props": {
        "className": "space-y-4"
      },
      "children": [
        {
          "type": "basic",
          "name": "P",
          "props": {
            "className": "text-label-subtle"
          },
          "text": "$t:sirsoft-ecommerce.admin.order.detail.modal.confirm_deposit.description"
        },
        {
          "comment": "결제예정금액 요약 (참고용)",
          "type": "basic",
          "name": "Div",
          "props": {
            "className": "rounded-lg border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-900 p-3 flex-between text-sm"
          },
          "children": [
            {
              "type": "basic",
              "name": "Span",
              "props": {
                "className": "text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400"
              },
              "text": "$t:sirsoft-ecommerce.admin.order.detail.modal.confirm_deposit.due_amount"
            },
            {
              "type": "basic",
              "name": "Span",
              "props": {
                "className": "font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100"
              },
              "text": "{{order.data?.total_due_amount_formatted ?? ''}}"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "comment": "입금자명 (선택)",
          "type": "basic",
          "name": "Div",
          "children": [
            {
              "type": "basic",
              "name": "Label",
              "props": {
                "className": "form-label-block"
              },
              "text": "$t:sirsoft-ecommerce.admin.order.detail.modal.confirm_deposit.depositor_name"
            },
            {
              "type": "basic",
              "name": "Input",
              "props": {
                "type": "text",
                "name": "depositor_name",
                "placeholder": "$t:sirsoft-ecommerce.admin.order.detail.modal.confirm_deposit.depositor_name_placeholder",
                "className": "text-primary w-full px-3 py-2 border border-gray-300 dark:border-gray-600 rounded-lg bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 text-sm focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-500 dark:focus:ring-blue-400 focus:border-blue-500 dark:focus:border-blue-400",
                "value": "{{_local.depositorName ?? ''}}"
              },
              "actions": [
                {
                  "type": "input",
                  "handler": "setState",
                  "params": {
                    "target": "local",
                    "depositorName": "{{$event.target.value}}"
                  }
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "comment": "입금액 (기본값 = 결제예정금액, 정확 일치 검증)",
          "type": "basic",
          "name": "Div",
          "children": [
            {
              "type": "basic",
              "name": "Label",
              "props": {
                "className": "form-label-block"
              },
              "children": [
                {
                  "type": "basic",
                  "name": "Span",
                  "text": "$t:sirsoft-ecommerce.admin.order.detail.modal.confirm_deposit.amount"
                },
                {
                  "type": "basic",
                  "name": "Span",
                  "props": {
                    "className": "text-required"
                  },
                  "text": "*"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "basic",
              "name": "Input",
              "props": {
                "type": "number",
                "name": "amount",
                "min": 0,
                "className": "{{_local.depositConfirmErrors?.amount ? 'w-full px-3 py-2 border border-red-500 dark:border-red-400 rounded-lg bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 text-gray-900 dark:text-white text-sm focus:ring-2 focus:ring-red-500 dark:focus:ring-red-400' : 'w-full px-3 py-2 border border-gray-300 dark:border-gray-600 rounded-lg bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 text-gray-900 dark:text-white text-sm focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-500 dark:focus:ring-blue-400 focus:border-blue-500 dark:focus:border-blue-400'}}",
                "value": "{{_local.depositAmount ?? 0}}"
              },
              "actions": [
                {
                  "type": "input",
                  "handler": "setState",
                  "params": {
                    "target": "local",
                    "depositAmount": "{{$event.target.value}}"
                  }
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "basic",
              "name": "Span",
              "if": "{{_local.depositConfirmErrors?.amount}}",
              "props": {
                "className": "form-error-xs mt-1 block"
              },
              "text": "{{_local.depositConfirmErrors?.amount?.[0] ?? ''}}"
            },
            {
              "type": "basic",
              "name": "Span",
              "if": "{{!_local.depositConfirmErrors?.amount}}",
              "props": {
                "className": "text-hint mt-1 block"
              },
              "text": "$t:sirsoft-ecommerce.admin.order.detail.modal.confirm_deposit.amount_hint"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "comment": "원 주문서 결제완료 처리 여부 — 체크 시 주문 상태를 결제완료로 전이(마일리지/재고/알림). 미체크 시 입금만 기록.",
          "type": "basic",
          "name": "Div",
          "props": {
            "className": "rounded-lg border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 p-3"
          },
          "children": [
            {
              "type": "basic",
              "name": "Label",
              "props": {
                "className": "flex items-start gap-2 cursor-pointer"
              },
              "children": [
                {
                  "type": "basic",
                  "name": "Input",
                  "props": {
                    "type": "checkbox",
                    "name": "mark_order_complete",
                    "className": "mt-0.5",
                    "checked": "{{_local.markOrderComplete ?? false}}"
                  },
                  "actions": [
                    {
                      "type": "change",
                      "handler": "setState",
                      "params": {
                        "target": "local",
                        "markOrderComplete": "{{$event.target.checked}}"
                      }
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "type": "basic",
                  "name": "Div",
                  "children": [
                    {
                      "type": "basic",
                      "name": "Span",
                      "props": {
                        "className": "text-primary text-sm font-medium block"
                      },
                      "text": "$t:sirsoft-ecommerce.admin.order.detail.modal.confirm_deposit.mark_order_complete"
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "basic",
                      "name": "Span",
                      "props": {
                        "className": "text-hint block"
                      },
                      "text": "$t:sirsoft-ecommerce.admin.order.detail.modal.confirm_deposit.mark_order_complete_hint"
                    }
                  ]
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "basic",
      "name": "Div",
      "props": {
        "className": "modal-footer-buttons"
      },
      "children": [
        {
          "type": "basic",
          "name": "Button",
          "props": {
            "type": "button",
            "className": "px-4 py-2 text-body border border-gray-300 dark:border-gray-600 rounded-lg hover:bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-800 dark:hover:bg-gray-700 disabled:opacity-50 disabled:cursor-not-allowed",
            "disabled": "{{_local.isConfirmingDeposit}}"
          },
          "actions": [
            {
              "type": "click",
              "handler": "closeModal"
            }
          ],
          "children": [
            {
              "type": "basic",
              "name": "Span",
              "text": "$t:sirsoft-ecommerce.admin.order.detail.modal.confirm_deposit.cancel"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "basic",
          "name": "Button",
          "props": {
            "type": "button",
            "className": "flex-center gap-2 px-4 py-2 text-sm bg-blue-600 dark:bg-blue-500 text-white rounded-lg hover:bg-blue-700 dark:hover:bg-blue-600 disabled:opacity-50 disabled:cursor-not-allowed",
            "disabled": "{{_local.isConfirmingDeposit}}"
          },
          "actions": [
            {
              "type": "click",
              "handler": "sirsoft-ecommerce.confirmDeposit",
              "params": {
                "orderId": "{{route.orderNumber}}",
                "amount": "{{_local.depositAmount}}",
                "depositorName": "{{_local.depositorName ?? ''}}",
                "markOrderComplete": "{{_local.markOrderComplete ?? false}}"
              }
            }
          ],
          "children": [
            {
              "type": "basic",
              "name": "Icon",
              "if": "{{_local.isConfirmingDeposit}}",
              "props": {
                "name": "spinner",
                "className": "animate-spin",
                "size": "sm"
              }
            },
            {
              "type": "basic",
              "name": "Span",
              "text": "$t:sirsoft-ecommerce.admin.order.detail.modal.confirm_deposit.confirm"
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}
